I raise this as an issue only because sometimes the wait person can make turn an unpleasant experience around by doing something 'special'.
But it apparently never occurred to her that she was an integral part of the 'dining experience.
'    Overall, our experience at TWCG was mediocre and in this price tier Houston's has them beat 10 to 1!
Maybe it is a good place for happy hour and a desert or maybe it's a 'date value' thing but I won't bother with it again.

