) and it was superb!
Came with a big whopping hunk of homemade cut fries--which I certainly didn't need but loved scarfing down like a hog!
Just fabulous quality of food here.
Their meat--and I mean the hamburger quality--is excellent, too, for what America offers (nothing compares to the beef in Argentina where I just returned from).
Love this place so much told the son to take a date there if he wants to impress her with good food.
